# Jest

Jest is a delightful JavaScript testing framework with zero configuration, built-in mocking, code coverage, and snapshot testing, maintained by Meta.

## Key Features

- **Zero configuration** - Works out of the box
- **Snapshot testing** - Track UI component changes
- **Built-in mocking** - Powerful mock functions and modules
- **Code coverage** - Built-in coverage reports
- **Watch mode** - Re-run tests on file changes
- **Parallel execution** - Fast test runs
- **Great errors** - Clear error messages and stack traces

## Use Cases

- React component testing
- Node.js application testing
- JavaScript unit testing
- Snapshot regression testing
- TypeScript testing

## Get Started with Jest

Delight in JavaScript testing with zero config. Visit [jestjs.io](https://jestjs.io) to implement comprehensive JavaScript testing.